WEBVTT

00:02.480 --> 00:05.790
Cheers is filmed
before a live studio audience.

00:05.960 --> 00:11.159
- All right, 1 955 AL MVP.
- Yogi Berra.

00:11.320 --> 00:13.390
All right, height of the left field wall
at Fenway.

00:13.560 --> 00:17.314
- The Green Monster is 37 feet high.
- Told you.

00:18.840 --> 00:20.068
All right, here you go.

00:20.240 --> 00:24.119
- lke Delock's lifetime ERA.
- 4:03. Had enough?

00:24.640 --> 00:27.393
Give it up, Norm. The woman's
a lean, mean trivia machine.

00:27.560 --> 00:29.676
- Unbelievable. You're the best.
- I know.

00:29.840 --> 00:31.956
- Ask me something.
- Forget it, Zeke.

00:32.119 --> 00:35.510
There aren't any questions
about wheat in there.

00:36.040 --> 00:38.395
Oh, and I suppose you know
everything that's in this book.

00:38.560 --> 00:40.039
- If it's in there, I know it.
- Yeah?

00:40.200 --> 00:42.236
- Yeah.
- Okay.

00:44.080 --> 00:48.835
What's the Library of Congress
card catalogue number?

00:49.920 --> 00:53.276
Seven, eight, zero, three,
four, seven, six.

00:53.480 --> 00:57.029
- That's not even close.
- What do you mean? Look there.

00:57.200 --> 00:58.872
What?

00:59.720 --> 01:02.234
That's it exactly.

