20:28.000 --> 20:31.709
That's just because we promised
to try to keep our distance.

20:31.880 --> 20:34.110
And we have.

20:34.280 --> 20:38.114
Our relationship has reached
the mature adult stage.

20:39.200 --> 20:41.589
Well, I wish there
were some way I could...

20:41.760 --> 20:43.637
...prove it to you.

20:45.160 --> 20:47.913
Well, maybe there is.

20:48.080 --> 20:50.958
Sit on my lap.

20:51.120 --> 20:54.271
I'm just trying to convince myself
that I can be close to a woman

20:54.440 --> 20:57.034
without it being sexual.

20:57.200 --> 21:01.432
- This is the silliest thing I've ever--
- Hey, come on, Diane.

21:03.400 --> 21:07.359
Well, if it'll help prove something
to you, all right.

21:12.880 --> 21:15.792
- Boy, you're nervous.
