22:55.240 --> 22:57.674
- Okay.
- Well, I think we've proved our point.

22:57.840 --> 23:00.195
Clearly we have
a nonsexual relationship.

23:00.360 --> 23:01.793
And you are a fine human being.

23:01.960 --> 23:03.916
- Well, thank you, Diane.
- So if you'll excuse me,

23:04.080 --> 23:06.958
